metadata.name: Sugimoto Vibes
metadata.description:
In late 2021 I was in a twitter space with 2 nft art legends @blockmuse and @ArtAsAnarchy where Art started to question me about my techniques and someone called Sugimoto. I had no idea who this was but it opened my mind to this great artist and style of photography. 

One day I hope to be on his level.

My first but not last offering in this style.
